(376, 1, '2022-10-10 17:00:17', '2022-10-10 17:00:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>International Cooperation Projects</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Responsible at the Algerian side of a CMEP project entitled ‘Agents intelligents: spécification formelle et application’. The responsible from the French side was Professor Guy Pierra, head of LISI laboratory at&nbsp;<strong>University of Poitiers</strong>&nbsp;2002 - 2006</li><li>Member of a CMEP&nbsp;project entitled ‘Optimisation combinatoire’. The responsible from the French side was Dr. Talbi El-Ghazali , member of LIFL laboratory at&nbsp;<strong>Lille University&nbsp;</strong>1999 - 2001</li><li>Responsible at the Algerian side of a CMEP project entitled&nbsp;‘Techniques de l’Intelligence Artificielle et Aspects des bases de données’.&nbsp;The responsible from the French side was Professor Daniel Kayser of LIPN laboratory at&nbsp;<strong>Villetaneuse University, Paris&nbsp;</strong>1996 - 1998</li><li>Principal investigator of a project entitled \'Dynamic ambulance dispatching and emergency calls covering in the context of COVID-19 crisis: The case of Saudi Arabia\' for<strong>&nbsp;Prince Mohammad bin Fahd Center for Futuristic Studies</strong>&nbsp;2021-2022</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Higher Ministry Technological Projects (Applied Research)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Head of project entitled&nbsp;‘Réalisation d’un entrepôt de données pour l’orientation des consommateurs vers les lieux de commerce spécialisé’ accredited for 4 years from 01/01/2016</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Higher Ministry PRFU Projects (Research for Education)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Head of project entitled ‘Développement de contenus numériques pour la ville d’Alger&nbsp;: Application au domaine du commerce.’