(462, 1, '2022-10-10 19:32:30', '2022-10-10 19:32:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Project (2017-2020)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research director of the PHC- Tassili cooperative project CMEP- USTHB and AIX-Marseille University, Code Campus France : 37502PG – Code MDU : 17MDU987. Title: \"Constraints, Data mining, Learning, Combinatorial Optimization and Applications\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>•&nbsp;Project (2022-2026)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research director of the National project PRFU: Title: “Techniques of machine learning and optimization by metaheuristics for solving complex problems,&nbsp;&nbsp;within the laboratory LRIA, C00L07UN160420220008.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>•&nbsp;Project (2018-2021)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research director of the National project PRFU: Title: “Intelligent optimization techniques and data mining for biological sequence analysis and prediction of protein structures. within the laboratory LRIA,&nbsp;C00L07UN160420180009.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(2014-2017) : Research director of the National project CNEPRU: Title: “Intelligent optimization techniques and data mining for biological sequence analysis and prediction of protein structures. within the laboratory LRIA, C00L07UN160420150004.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>•&nbsp;(2014-2017) : Research director of the National project CNEPRU. Title: “Local search methods for difficult combinatorial problems, within the laboratory LRIA, B*00220130007.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>•&nbsp;Project (2010-2013) Research Member in the National project PNR, within the laboratory LRIA.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>•&nbsp;Project (2007-2010)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research Member in the N