(612, 1, '2022-10-10 22:28:04', '2022-10-10 22:28:04', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Organisateur:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Humboldt-Universität zu Berlin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Résumé:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our goal with ICSB 2022 is to re-ignite the vibrant field of systems biology. We have selected a set of topics and speakers we think can excite you all and we hope you will enjoy our great city and the programme.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our line-up of keynotes and session chairs/speakers is amazing and we encourage you all to submit talks and posters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please join us in making ICSB 2022 the best ICSB ever. We are going all in on trying to reboot the community after the pandemic. This meeting will be in person and full of exciting science!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Call website can be found here on the EasyChair platform:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://easychair.org/cfp/ICSB2022\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://easychair.org/cfp/ICSB2022\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The main conference website is https://www.icsb2022.berlin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Global INBOX; &nbsp; &nbsp; Email.: info@icsb2022.berlin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sujets:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MULTI-SCALE MODELS, MACHINE LEARNING / ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE, ALPHA FOLD, DEEP HIDDEN PHYSICS, SINGLE CELL MODELING, WHOLE CELL MODELING, TUMOR ECOSYSTEMS, SIGNAL TRANSDUCTION, CANCER SYSTEMS BIOLOGY, COMPUTATIONAL PATHOLOGY, IMAGING ALGORITHMS, NETWORK BIOLOGY &amp; PRECISION MEDICINE, MICROBIOMES, CLI